==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Healthless
<hw>Health"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Without health,
whether of body or mind; infirm.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧A <xex>healthless</xex> or
old age.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Jer. Taylor.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not conducive to health; unwholesome.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Healthlessness</ent>⟦br⟧
